      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": true,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Product Information",
        "text": "<h2>Product Information</h2><p>The All-In-One Serum brightens, plumps & smooths the look of skin using a unique blend of active ingredients:</p><ul><li><strong>Niacinamide</strong> clarifies and evens tone, refines pores, calms redness</li><li><strong>Retinol and Bakuchiol</strong> boost cell turnover and collagen production, reducing fine lines, wrinkles, and pigmentation</li><li><strong>Lactic and Mandelic Acids</strong> gently exfoliate to smooth texture and enhance radiance</li><li><strong>Argireline® Peptides</strong> reduce wrinkle depth by up to 48% in clinical use</li><li><strong>Ethyl Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C) and Ferulic Acid</strong> brightens and protect against oxidative damage</li><li><strong>Hyaluronic Acid</strong> delivers lasting hydration, plumping fine lines and smoothing skin</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_4HMtMy": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Usage Instructions",
        "text": "<h2>Usage Instructions</h2><p><strong>How To Use:</strong></p><ol><li>After cleansing, apply 1-2 pumps to cleansed skin (face and neck).</li><li>Use every second night during the first two weeks of use whilst your skin builds tolerance.</li><li>Use daily for best results.</li></ol>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_Daptpc": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Product Claims",
        "text": "<h2>Product Claims & User Study</h2><p>Key claims:</p><ul><li>Targets uneven texture, fine lines, and discoloration with clinically-backed ingredients that work together to smooth, firm, and visibly brighten your skin over time.</li><li>Contains active ingredients such as retinol and niacinamide to help reduce the visibility of wrinkles and age spots, and smooth skin texture.</li><li>Deeply hydrates skin to make fine lines less visible for more plumper, younger looking skin.</li><li>Even skin tone for a more radiant complexion, and reduces the appearance of dark spots and help to prevent discoloration with continued use.</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_6LUnay": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "blocks": {
        "quote_KxAi43": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "style": "blue",
            "text": "<p>Remember to <strong>add a personal touch</strong> to the messaging, talk about how the filter makes your skin feel.</p><p>Examples:</p><ul><li>“This serum gave me my glow back.”</li><li>“Nothing else has faded my dark spots like this.”</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
